# ============================================================
#  playing_cards .gitignore  (重複排除・統合済み)
# ============================================================

# --- Windows / WSL Zone Identifier files ---
# *Zone.Identifier が "x:Zone.Identifier" / 素の "Zone.Identifier" も内包する。
*Zone.Identifier
*.Identifier

# --- Android build artifacts ---
**/android_index_*.html

# --- Dependencies / build outputs (どの階層でも) ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.vite/

# playing_cards 固有のビルド出力（**/dist/ では拾えない別名）
dist-android/
dist-enpc/
dist-subpath-test/

# scripts/ は独立した nested git repo（tarball backup に含む）
scripts/

# --- Env ---
.env
.env.*
**/.env

# --- Local tooling / caches / 検証エビデンス (リポジトリに入れない) ---
.claude/settings.local.json
.playwright-mcp/
**/test-results/
**/playwright-report/
screenshots_log/
undefined/

# --- IDE / OS ---
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Logs / temp / archives ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*.swp
*.pyc
*.tar.gz

# --- Secrets / keystores (global) ---
*.jks
*.keystore
key.properties
keystore.properties

# --- Media (大容量はコミットしない) ---
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.mkv
*.webm

# --- Reserved / misc ---
NUL
**/NUL
*.iml
